SET NOCOUNT ON;
DECLARE @inserted0 TABLE ([Id] uniqueidentifier, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [ProjectFiles] USING (
VALUES (@p0, @p1, @p2, @p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, @p7, @p8, 0),
(@p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, @p14, @p15, @p16, @p17, 1),
(@p18, @p19, @p20, @p21, @p22, @p23, @p24, @p25, @p26, 2),
(@p27, @p28, @p29, @p30, @p31, @p32, @p33, @p34, @p35, 3),
(@p36, @p37, @p38, @p39, @p40, @p41, @p42, @p43, @p44, 4),
(@p45, @p46, @p47, @p48, @p49, @p50, @p51, @p52, @p53, 5)) AS i ([AddDate], [AddUserId], [DeleteDate], [DeleteUserId], [FileName], [IsActive], [ProjectId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([AddDate], [AddUserId], [DeleteDate], [DeleteUserId], [FileName], [IsActive], [ProjectId], [UpdateDate], [UpdateUserId])
VALUES (i.[AddDate], i.[AddUserId], i.[DeleteDate], i.[DeleteUserId], i.[FileName], i.[IsActive], i.[ProjectId], i.[UpdateDate], i.[UpdateUserId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[IsDeleted] FROM [ProjectFiles] t
INNER JOIN @inserted0 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

    SELECT TOP(@__TypedProperty_2) [p].[Id], [p].[AddDate], [p].[BathroomCount], [p].[CityId], [p].[CurrencyId], [p].[Description], [p].[DescriptionDe], [p].[DescriptionRu], [p].[DescriptionTranslateKey], [p].[DistrictId], [p].[Floor], [p].[FloorCount], [p].[GrossArea], [p].[IsActive], [p].[IsFavourite], [p].[IsRent], [p].[IsSold], [p].[NetArea], [p].[Price], [p].[PriceEur], [p].[ProjectDate], [p].[ProjectEndDate], [p].[ProjectNumber], [p].[ProjectStatus], [p].[ProjectTye], [p].[SaloonCount], [p].[SeeClose], [p].[StreetId], [p].[Title], [p].[TitleDe], [p].[TitleRu], [p].[TitleTranslateKey], [p].[TownId], [p].[Year], [p].[ZipCode]

    ORDER BY [p].[AddDate] DESC
